'''Gyousatsu''' ([[Japanese]]: 行殺) means a quick or effortless kill. The term is most frequently used in video games, anime, and "action" literature.

'''Gyousatsu Shinkengumi''' is a [[doujin soft|doujin]] PC strategy game.

'''Gyousatsu! Spirits''' is a [[doujin soft|doujin]] PC fighting game based on '''Gyousatsu Shinkengumi'''.

